  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Line a baking dish with parchment paper for easy cleanup.",
    "Add the frozen seafood mix, fresh parsley, fresh dill, garlic powder, lemon juice, and olive oil to the prepared baking dish.",
    "Mix well to combine, ensuring the seafood is evenly coated with the seasonings.",
    "Dot the top of the seafood mixture with butter.",
    "Sprinkle crushed grains of paradise and fresh thyme over the seafood for added flavor and crunch.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Cover the baking dish with aluminum foil and bake for 15 minutes.",
    "Remove the foil and continue baking for an additional 10-12 minutes, or until the seafood is cooked through and golden brown.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh chives before serving.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
